![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/48d935ec-dd92-4599-a148-0c036a8d96d5/ep236.jpg?format=original)

The Umbrella Academy is BACK but is it a return to form? Join us as we discuss the third season of one of the wildest comic book shows out right now. We'll discuss character motivations, debate motives, and talk all about the Apocalypse in this in-depth review of Season 3. Kick off your Sunday shoes, put that cat in the cradle and join us in the house of the rising sun as we fall back in love with the world's most dysfunctional superhero family!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

  
